%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant FS as File System
    participant SP as matching specialist<br/>subagent

    User->>Claude: /update-api-contracts-docs <area> [path]

    note over Claude: Capture timestamps

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Preflight
    Claude->>FS: Check .claude/docs/reference-api-contracts.md exists
    FS-->>Claude: present / absent
    alt reference doc absent
        Claude->>User: reference-api-contracts.md not found<br/>Run /create-api-contracts-docs first
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end
    Claude->>FS: Read api-contracts-analysis.json (get roots)
    FS-->>Claude: {frontend_roots, backend_roots, primary_style}

    note over Claude,SP: Phase: Re-run specialist
    Claude->>SP: Invoke <area> specialist with<br/>{frontend_roots, backend_roots, primary_style}
    SP-->>Claude: {axis, findings} or SKIP

    note over Claude: Phase: Merge
    Claude->>FS: Read current reference-api-contracts.md
    FS-->>Claude: current content
    Claude->>Claude: Replace only <area> section(s)<br/>Preserve all other sections verbatim
    opt area is http or auth
        Claude->>Claude: Prepare api-data-flow.mmd diff
    end
    Claude->>Claude: Patch api-contracts-analysis.json <area> key

    note over Claude,User: Phase: User confirmation
    Claude->>User: Section diff for <area>:<br/>[before] vs [after]<br/>[1] Accept [2] Abort
    User-->>Claude: choice
    alt abort
        break Skill aborts — no writes
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Write
    Claude->>FS: Write merged reference-api-contracts.md
    FS-->>Claude: OK
    Claude->>FS: Patch api-contracts-analysis.json
    FS-->>Claude: OK
    opt diagram updated
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/sequences/api-data-flow.mmd
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Report
    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/state/reports/update-api-contracts-docs-<ts>.md
    FS-->>Claude: OK
    Claude->>User: Updated: <area> section refreshed<br/>Endpoints before/after: N→M
